lead_paragraph: Dez Bryant appeared in the locker room Thursday and seemed to be in a good mood, which was more than the Dallas receiver could say for the first two days of the week.

headline.print_headline: WR Bryant Avoided Cowboys for 2 Days, Fearing News on Knee
